The Municipal Accountant should coordinate with the heads of the implementing office in returning to the source agencies, the excess amount from completed projects; and

The Municipal Accountant should also secure MOAs on all funds received and other pertinent information so as to facilitate the proper control of its utilization and accounting treatment of its transactions.

